Complete type definitions for IRC plugin:

```typescript
import type {
  BlockStreamingCoalesceConfig,
  DmConfig,
  DmPolicy,
  GroupPolicy,
  GroupToolPolicyBySenderConfig,
  GroupToolPolicyConfig,
  MarkdownConfig,
  OpenClawConfig,
  BaseProbeResult,
