// Private runtime barrel for the bundled PulseBoard extension.
// Keep this barrel thin and aligned with the local extension surface.
//
// PulseBoard does not have a dedicated openclaw/plugin-sdk/pulseboard facade, so
// we import from individual public SDK subpaths and implement any missing helpers
// locally.

